Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: Three components to the Oshawa Centre: Galleria, Central Office and Executive Centre.  Close proximity to Highway 401.  Walking distance to Public transit (Go and Durham Region Transit).  Numerous amenities within Oshawa Centre including retail stores, GoodLife Fitness Centre, restaurants and food court.  Exceptional free parking.  Full renovation of Executive Centre lobby.  On-site property management.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: 419 King Street West - Oshawa Centre, Executive Centre
